<div style="margin:0;padding:0;background:#eef0f3;">
  <table role="presentation" width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="background:#eef0f3;padding:24px 0;">
    <tr><td align="center">
      <table role="presentation" width="600" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="max-width:600px;width:100%;background:#ffffff;border-radius:10px;overflow:hidden;font-family:'Segoe UI','Microsoft JhengHei','PingFang TC',Arial,sans-serif;color:#1f2933;box-shadow:0 1px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);">
        <tr>
          <td style="background:#b91c1c;padding:18px 28px;color:#ffffff;">
            <div style="font-size:19px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:.5px;">&#9888;&#65039; 資訊安全警示 &middot; Security Alert</div>
            {% if org_name %}
            <div style="font-size:12px;opacity:.85;margin-top:3px;">{{ org_name }} 資訊安全中心</div>
            {% endif %}
          </td>
        </tr>
        <tr><td style="padding:26px 28px 8px;">
          <p style="margin:0 0 12px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.6;">{{ user }} 您好,</p>
          <p style="margin:0 0 20px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.7;">
            系統偵測到您的帳號自 <strong>{{ location }}</strong> 的 IP 建立了一次 VPN（IPsec）連線。
            基於帳號安全,特此通知您確認是否為您本人操作。
          </p>
          <table role="presentation" width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="border-collapse:collapse;margin:0 0 22px;font-size:14px;">
            <tr>
              <td style="padding:10px 12px;background:#f5f6f8;border:1px solid #e4e7eb;width:130px;color:#52606d;">帳號 Account</td>
              <td style="padding:10px 12px;border:1px solid #e4e7eb;"><strong>{{ user }}</strong></td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td style="padding:10px 12px;background:#f5f6f8;border:1px solid #e4e7eb;color:#52606d;">來源 IP</td>
              <td style="padding:10px 12px;border:1px solid #e4e7eb;">{{ ip }}</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td style="padding:10px 12px;background:#f5f6f8;border:1px solid #e4e7eb;color:#52606d;">來源位置 Location</td>
              <td style="padding:10px 12px;border:1px solid #e4e7eb;">{{ location }}</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td style="padding:10px 12px;background:#f5f6f8;border:1px solid #e4e7eb;color:#52606d;">時間 Time</td>
              <td style="padding:10px 12px;border:1px solid #e4e7eb;">{{ time }}</td>
            </tr>
          </table>
          <table role="presentation" width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="border-collapse:collapse;margin:0 0 12px;">
            <tr><td style="padding:12px 14px;background:#ecfdf3;border-left:4px solid #12b76a;border-radius:4px;font-size:14px;line-height:1.6;">
              <strong style="color:#027a48;">&#10004; 若確認是您本人操作</strong><br>
              無須採取任何行動,可直接忽略本通知。
            </td></tr>
          </table>
          <table role="presentation" width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="border-collapse:collapse;margin:0 0 20px;">
            <tr><td style="padding:12px 14px;background:#fef3f2;border-left:4px solid #f04438;border-radius:4px;font-size:14px;line-height:1.6;">
              <strong style="color:#b42318;">&#9888; 若「不是」您本人操作</strong><br>
              您的帳號可能已遭盜用,請立即：
              <ol style="margin:8px 0 0;padding-left:20px;">
                <li>變更您的網域（AD）密碼。</li>
                <li>通報資訊安全單位協助確認。</li>
              </ol>
              {% if security_contact %}
              <div style="margin-top:8px;">聯絡窗口：<strong>{{ security_contact }}</strong></div>
              {% endif %}
            </td></tr>
          </table>
        </td></tr>
        <tr><td style="padding:16px 28px 24px;border-top:1px solid #eef0f3;">
          <p style="margin:0;font-size:12px;color:#7b8794;line-height:1.6;">
            本信由系統自動發送,請勿直接回覆。<br>
            This is an automated security notification. Please do not reply.
            {% if org_name %}<br>—— {{ org_name }}{% endif %}
          </p>
        </td></tr>
      </table>
    </td></tr>
  </table>
</div>
